{The endgame looks unpleasant for White. His own pawns present no danger,
whereas the black pawns look very menacing. To discover the most secure
defence it is essential to possess a solid knowledge of the endgame, which
Morphy now exhibits. ---} 40. Bxa3 $1 {Calculating that he cannot be prevented
from reaching a 'fortress' position.} bxa3 41. Kd4 Bxf4 42. Kxc4 Bxh2 43. Kb3
Bd6 44. Kc2 {. Reaching a theoretical draw; the white king cannot be dislodged
from b1 and c2.} 1/2-1/2

